        "roll": "3",
        "rollType": "result",
        "rollTarget": 0,
        "blindroll": false,
        "description": "<p>Trolls are very hard to kill, for they regenerate [[/r 3 #The Troll's wounds close, healing this many hp...]] points of damage each round, unless the damage is from fire or acid. If a troll loses a limb or body part, these parts will attempt to crawl or squirm back toward the main portion of the body to reattach. A troll can reattach a severed member instantly by holding it to the stump. Due to this powerful ability to regenerate, trolls cannot be permanently destroyed except by fire or acid. If a troll is damaged enough to be killed (reaches 0 or fewer hit points) the troll will continue to regenerate and stand again to fight when it regenerates to 1 or more hp. When confronted by fire or acid, a troll's morale drops to 0.</p>",
        "save": ""
      },
